Title: Blood
Plot: When several violent deaths in a small farming community are connected by the destruction of digital devices, Mulder believes that people are being driven to kill by the use of subliminal messages in the digital readouts.
GuestStars: William Sanderson, John Cygan, Kimberly Patton, George Touliatos, John Harris, Gerry Rousseau, William Mackenzie, Diana Stevan, David Fredericks, Kathleen Duborg, B.J. Harrison, Andre Daniels
